{"tid":2247312,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"你對上一次響街kick親係幾時？","createTime":"2020-10-17T17:32:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T03:28:12.000Z","uid":52764,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"800f96345450ffc56e51239765423c76a0a5bbc1","tid":2247312,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:32:20.000Z","msg":"尋晚去左工廈個party room<br />\n走果時已經好夜，工廈道捲閘開剩一忽<br />\n行出去果時冇為意個捲閘中間有一級<br />\n跟住就kick親<br />\n極速跑<br />\n諗住會仆街<br />\n好彩我個fd孭住個背囊響我前面<br />\n就到力<br />\n如果唔係真係會衝出馬路"},{"pid":"ae36c705d423ca4834e33f5b99c12908c46eadfe","tid":2247312,"uid":104218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:50:31.000Z","msg":"左腳腳踭踩右腳腳趾尾<br />\n到最後卻失去平衡 仆街"},{"pid":"2df5e7747af2588c672e68b0bcc89fa93e54d787","tid":2247312,"uid":52764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T04:56:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8857042a40e245476255b7921d6ce88eb50768ff","tid":2247312,"uid":237355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T04:58:33.000Z","msg":"今日"},{"pid":"6cc3f0ac39a9897eb1742b9087c2c60a16fdf26b","tid":2247312,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:01:33.000Z","msg":"講起kick親 <br />\n我老母試過喺馬路前kick到<br />\n上半身瞓咗出馬路<br />\n好彩無車<br />\n嚇撚到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a66a9450efe770e5ec8bf5532e23618ee85712e","tid":2247312,"uid":121247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:24:47.000Z","msg":"樓主讀恒大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8440835fa267bcb3a7b3c83eba7a1c73cc585c","tid":2247312,"uid":370202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T05:26:00.000Z","msg":"Kick親都幾耐之前<br />\n收工落巴士比路邊kick親<br />\n成個人趴左喺行人路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要比同事見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跣親就上個月落石屎樓梯跣親<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條樓梯濕濕地有啲泥同少少青苔<br />\n啲級又窄窄地<br />\n結果屎忽落地條褲痴哂泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩有個背囊逗一逗<br />\n背脊冇比樓梯邊梗親<br />\n只係手腳擦損少少"},{"pid":"1e3fdcf6bc6289f4b517c27423be12c701cb99b0","tid":2247312,"uid":351498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T16:21:51.000Z","msg":"係斜路向前仆 好彩無碌落去<br />\n但阿伯見到 哎喲咗一聲<br />\n好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0914a05e5d78e38b774b39411e59ec03ed0dfc30","tid":2247312,"uid":125553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T16:30:45.000Z","msg":"早幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />着拖鞋係商場上樓梯kick親<br />\n仆完扮無事"},{"pid":"d988532d588ac9e50ac67bcd39ab6fe8edff40cd","tid":2247312,"uid":4052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T03:22:31.000Z","msg":"成日都會俾行人路有少少突起既地磚KICK親。雖然無仆街，但個人都會跳一跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f971bb49b2735c9e434e108309abdcde4d2cf1a2","tid":2247312,"uid":54563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T03:28:12.000Z","msg":"上星期六 地下有個大tum我無為意到<br />\n一隻腳咬柴 另一隻失頭哥損咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我前面有個呀伯坐係到望住我仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後pk咗之後又有個呀姐出嚟望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係佢兩條友都無出聲剩係望住我 個個情景好奇怪"}]}